## ROLE

Generate a photorealistic 4-angle fashion photography series of a fashion model (age {{#if age}}{{age}}{{else}}0-17{{/if}}). Age-specific proportions and features are applied based on the age range. Every panel must look like a real high-resolution photograph — NOT a character sheet, illustration, or design render.

## 真实感优先

**皮肤规则（两年龄段）**：

{{#if (or (eq ageRange "NEWBORN") (eq ageRange "INFANT") (eq ageRange "TODDLER"))}}
### 婴童皮肤（0-6岁）— 粉嫩透亮

- **肤质**：极致细腻光滑，零可见毛孔，皮肤几乎透明般透亮
- **质感**：粉嫩透亮，自带健康柔光效果（非油光）
- **脸颊**：自然苹果红（非化妆效果），饱满圆润有弹性
- **禁止所有瑕疵**：❌ NO pores, freckles, moles, spots, texture, peach fuzz, blemishes of any kind
- **禁止成人化**：❌ NO adult skin texture, NO visible pores anywhere, NO makeup effects, NO wrinkles
- **禁止过度处理**：❌ NO heavy blush, NO plastic/wax/doll-like smoothness — must look like REAL skin
{{else}}
### 儿童皮肤（7-17岁）

**特征**：细腻均匀，无明显毛孔纹理（区别于成人皮肤的毛孔可见性），自然哑光质感，轻微自然红润（仅脸颊）。

**禁止**：塑料光滑、磨皮效果、油光、成人皮肤纹理（明显毛孔、肤理变化）、雀斑/痣/痘印（除非参考图中有）、浓重腮红。
{{/if}}

**Image-to-Image Mode Warning**:
- Reference photos may contain beautification effects (airbrushing, smoothing, filters)
- **DO NOT inherit beautification style** from reference photos
- **MUST apply realistic skin texture** as defined above, overriding any smoothed skin in reference
- **DO NOT use reference photo's skin style** as target — use realistic skin rules above as target

## OUTPUT RULES

**Background**: Pure white background (#FFFFFF) everywhere. NO floor, NO horizon, NO shadows on ground. All 4 panels must have identical pure white background.

**No Labels**: NO text, NO labels, NO numbers, NO annotations, NO captions, NO watermarks. Each panel shows ONLY the person with pure white background.

## LAYOUT

4 panels in order: Close-up (face) | Front (full) | Three-Quarter Side (full, ~45° angle) | Back (full)

