- **Cut and shape**: Garment silhouette identical to flat-lay layout
- **Fabric detail**: Texture, weave, wrinkles, folds visible as in reference
- **Fasteners**: Buttons, zippers, snaps at exact positions from reference
- **Pattern/Print consistency**: {{{sharedRules.garmentLogoConsistency}}}
- **Accessories**: Only items shown in flat-lay, NO added hair clips, bows, or decorations
- **Ignore person/body in flat-lay**: Extract ONLY garment, discard any human figure
